item.title: Tony Orlando & Dawn - Tie a Yellow Ribbon Round the Ole Oak Tree - Key of F - BruderMaister
item.description: Play along video for the song Tie a Yellow Ribbon Round the Ole Oak Tree by Tony Orlando & Dawn from the channel BruderMaister. Chords used in the song: A7, Am, B♭m, C7, Cm, D7, Dm, F, G7, Gm, Gm7.
